## Design Choices

- **Dark theme** (`#080b14` background) — premium govtech/fintech feel
- **Teal + Blue gradient** as primary brand colour — trust + technology
- **Gold accent** for warnings/officials — authority and importance
- **Violet** for judiciary — gravitas
- **Space Grotesk** (headings) + **Inter** (body) — modern, legible
- **Scroll-triggered animations** — elements fade up as they enter viewport; hero elements animate in on load
- **Floating hero image badges** — "Verified on-chain", "NADRA Biometric ✓", "IPFS Stored"
